{"tid":944242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大聯院會促李國章退位","createTime":"2018-12-17T04:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T04:46:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"924c6f353f2fb1c6a807d8a3135d0e757313c0a9","tid":944242,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181217/20570465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F20570465&d=bCSnapzdQItT%2Fed9Rpo7b49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e479996c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F20570465&h=d7d72284\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181217/20570465</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月17日 <br />\n<br />\n港大聯院會促李國章退位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181217/large/17la2p9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181217%2Flarge%2F17la2p9.jpg&h=b5982138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【校委會連任風波】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港大學校委會主席李國章（圖），上周五獲政府刊憲續任三年，旋即引起校內反彈。港大學生會聯院會昨日發表題為「劣跡昭著再登殿　眾望難孚應讓賢」的公開聲明，譴責政府再度漠視學生聲音，無視李國章剛愎自用而力不勝任，多年來不斷與學生及教職員為敵。聲明又批評，由李國章續任校委會主席，「實乃我校之恥之辱」，公開呼籲李退位讓賢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥特首漠視學生意見<br />\n<br />\n有份參與聯署聲明組織，包括該校學生會建築學會、文學院學生會、經濟及工商管理學會、牙醫學會、教育學會、工程學會、法律學會、醫學會、理學會及社會科學學會。港大學生會聯院會強調，李國章無開誠布公面對師生的勇氣、無廣納百川聆聽意見的器量、亦無明辨是非維護自主的承擔；批評李國章自出任該校校委以來，屢次口出狂言，完全不尊重港大學生與教職員，「卑劣之處為整個港大社群所不齒」。<br />\n<br />\n聯院會又質疑，特首作為必然校監，掌任命校委會成員之大權，卻一再漠視學生意見，是借制度之便將香港大學玩弄於股掌。<br />\n<br />\n聲明要求廢除校監必然制，並重新檢討校委會主席任命程序，同時公開呼籲李國章「反躬自省，退位讓賢」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n西環集中營：梁振英疑聽命收聲 (季陶)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日提醒你：《人地刊物．我地刊物》第三回展覽"},{"pid":"5540b1e0f72c20eedc70fab2e2a624ba43c05134","tid":944242,"uid":208159,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"347db3e2f864428e02673758103a218b5901d135","tid":944242,"uid":208159,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:26:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa3522aee7fcf52feb81276524a90210c5c7ca4a","tid":944242,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"而家明係玩鳩你呀，吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實成個香港都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2ebc54ef9a8de254831961e51b278577546b6d","tid":944242,"uid":208159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0559dfe97556de86db9e133f82f099ce0c465553","tid":944242,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa3522aee7fcf52feb81276524a90210c5c7ca4a","tid":944242,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"而家明係玩鳩你呀，吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實成個香港都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"全世界都係咁醜惡"},{"pid":"cff6b3490fdb164a8881d12bfcb14887b325ed97","tid":944242,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 自在人生 )"},{"pid":"e7c69d605167e74a39578fecafd3dba0d403a361","tid":944242,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5445865d05b187c376b8b5bb4f23dd9c545b980","tid":944242,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}